.SH "DESCRIPTION"
\*[self] is an adaptation of Peter Palfrader's code2html perl package.
It accepts input from STDIN or from an input_file. The language mode is
guessed from the input and the file name. If this is not correct, it can
be changed using the -l option. Language modes provided are:
